Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.70,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Even though it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:22.23,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…even though I feel sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:29.24,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…in the court I feel just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:37.48,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,When I hear the ball flying, my heart races.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:41.59,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Receive. Toss. Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:46.51,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:49.49,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,But sometimes I cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:52.52,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,I'm a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:01:00.68,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Through the tears and sweat, putting up a youthful fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:08.76,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…under the blue sky, I just want to scream:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:16.86,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:26.12,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王の出会い}Episode 007\NMeeting The Big Four
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{私達は公開試合で始めての勝利を掴み。}For the first time, we've won a public game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆生まれ変わったように自身を取り戻した。}Everyone regained their confidence as if they were born anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、も一度。}One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{トス。}Toss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい、今までのバレー部とは違うと思うね。}I think our club has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX始めて勝ったんだもん。}We've got our own first victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{今までとは違うのよ。}It feels different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、サンキュー。}Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう一本。}One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆、バレーはチームワークよね。}Volleyball is about teamwork, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう。}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見学園バレー部のチームワークは日本一なんて。}Fujimi volleyball club's teamwork is the best in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXも強い。}My hunger's strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、皆。}All right, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{もうそろそろはXXXの終わる時間よ。}The warm-up time is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生がXXXるわ。}Professor Hongou gets back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、部室へ行きましょう。}Let's go to the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーOK。\Nーそれ！}- OK.\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーごめん、ごめん。\Nーま、努さんじゃない。}- Sorry, sorry.\N- Oh, it's Tsutomu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの、そんなに慌てて。}Why are you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{新聞部の緊急集会なんだ。}Newspaper club has emergency meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{落ち着いてよ。}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなことじゃ優秀な新聞部員とは言えないわよ。}It doesn't suit a good newspaper club member such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併。}It's the merge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併なんだよ。}We're merging…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併?}Merging?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま…一体何が？}Who's merging with whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{学園の上に今まで色んな問題があったことは君達もう知ってるだろ。}The academy's upper management has a lot of problems. You heard about it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{学園のXXXに比べて、生徒の数が少ないんだ。}Most of them stem out of the low student numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{つまり、授業料やそなたを場合にしても、色んな経費は掛かってやっていけない時代に来てんだ。}Even with our tuition fees, the school recently cannot afford many expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{それで今、職員会XX、合併することが発表されたんだよ。}So just now the board has decided that we'll merge with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併て、どんな学校と？}Who will we merge with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{や、それが分からない。}That I still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、急ぐから。}Well, I'm in a hurry. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{生徒の数が少ないから、経営が上手くいかないなんて。}Just because there's few students, the management goes bonkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{市立の学校何て情けないもんだよね。}Municipal schools are going to the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併って？}What does merging mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{他の学校と一緒に成ることよ。}It means joining with another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなことが分かってるわ。}We know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{一緒成ってどう成るかってことよ。}She's asking how it's going to look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはよく分かんないわ。}I'm not really sure myself either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併すると富士見学園じゃ無くなっちゃうでしょう？}When we merge, there will be no more Fujimi Academy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{そーそんなバカな。}That… that's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{学校が無くなっちゃうなんとこと。あるはずないわよ。}I can't imagine the school to disappear. There's no way it'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{だけどさ、今までの学園とは違うものに成っちゃうだろうさ。}But the academy will certainly change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{お？}Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生！}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー先生！\Nー先生！}- Professor!\N- Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当なんですか？合併て言うのわ。}Is it true? The whole merging thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生、どこの学校とか(XXX・結論)です？}Professor, which school are we merging with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは未だ…決まってない。}That's still… undecided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、富士見学園が無くなっちゃうの？}Does it mean Fujimi Academy will be no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ…それは未だ…}That… that's still…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{その学校にもバレー部あるんだろうし、バレー部にどうなっちゃうんですか？}If that school has a volleyball club too, what will happen to ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言う形で合併するか…}The exact form of the merge…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{それも未だ決まっていないだ。}…is still undecided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{折角纏まりかけた時に、又問題が…}Just when we've united, more troubles…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうなるかしら。}I wonder what happens now…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ…}Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{とんでもいいから、早くはっきりした欲しいわね。}Whatever it is, let it happen already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{学校とはどう成るか、バレー部どう成るのか。}I mean both the school and our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの人達は…}These girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたち。富士見学園のバレー部ね。}You. You're Fujimi Academy's volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。それはどうかしたの?}Correct. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{ハハハハハ。}Hahahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中学の人達ね。}They're from Hamaki middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたち…バレー部ね。}You're from volleyball club too, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{「あなたたち…バレー部ね。」}"You're from volleyball club too, no?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって。}…she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{こいつは参った、がっくりね。}Gee, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}My.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちを知らないの？}Don't you know us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{無理ないわよ。}I can't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{大会の第一試合で消えただったもん。}You dropped out the first in the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうね。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{一番弱いことじゃない?}It makes you the best losers, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{待ちなさいよ。}Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、何か。}Whoa, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{まさか「あたしたちと試合しよう」って言うんじゃないでしょうね。}You're not going to beg us for a match now, are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{ハハハハハ。}Hahahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーちょっと。\Nー止しなさい、カッコ。}- Hold on…\N- Let her be, Kakko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{選手権大会で浜紀中学は…}Actually, Hamaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{…準優勝だったわね。}…was placed second in the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{桂城さんだは？}Katsuragi-san, is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{何があったの、あの人達と？}What's the deal with these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいえ、別に。}Nothing particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの人達を知っている？}Do you know these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいえ。}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの四人よ。}It's those four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{無名の学校優勝決定まで進めて、一躍有名にした浜紀中学バレー部の四天王と言うのわ。}Based in an unknown school, they advanced to the finals and quickly became known as Hamaki volleyball club's "Big Four".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王？}"Big Four"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれが浜紀中学の四天王なの…}So they're the Hamaki's Big Four…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{噂には聞いてたは…}I've heard rumors…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの四人のコンビ攻撃は素晴らしいって評判ね。}Their attack duo is famed to be excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{学園はどう成っちゃう分からないなんて…}I don't know what'll happen to our school…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな気分じゃ、練習もうできないわね。}I don't feel like practicing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{練習休まXXいけないわよ。}We shouldn't take breaks from the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、キャプテン？}Right, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン！}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{大変よ！}Troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{なによ？}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併の相手が決まったんだって。}They decided who will be merging with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXとか浜紀中学と合併するんだってさ。}It's the Hamaki middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中学と？}Hamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中学とこっちをつってくるんですってさ。}Hamaki is coming to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、バレー部は？}What about the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの四天王と一緒に成るのよ。}The Big Four comes to us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{よいっしょ。}Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、良いわよ。}All right, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、遅刻よ。}Hey, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめん、ごめん。}Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{あのね、桂城さん今日練習できないって。}Hey, Katsuragi-san's not coming to practice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{卒業式なんても、XXXの感じXXXあるんだって。}She's soon going to graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{もうすぐ卒業式ね。}Graduation, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{桂城さんはいなくなると寂しく成るわね。}It'll be lonely without Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{その代わりに入ってくるのは浜紀中学の四天王なんて。}In exchange, we'll have Himaki's Big Four join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{厳しくなるわね。}It'll get tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、それから本郷先生…}Ah, also, professor Hongou…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{職員会は長く成りそうだから…}…since the teachers meeting seems to prolong…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{練習を始めておくよう言って。}…he told us to start by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、始めるわよ。}All right then, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{張り切って行こう。}Let's go at it with full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中学の四天王何かに負けないようにさ。}We can't lose to Hamaki's Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{おう。負けてたまるもんか。}Yeah. We won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんな四天王XXXさ。}Not to these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい、ファイト。}Fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、もう一本。}One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{し…四天王？}Th… The Big Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン。}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{来た。}They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{ままじゃない。}So-so, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXは新しそうだ。}Equipment looks new too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{思ったより、良い体育館ね。}Just as expected, you've got a nice gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{これなら、十分練習できるわ。}We should be able to practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{中々(XXX・いかして)(XXX・見じゃん)。}I want to try it out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうかのチームじゃXXXされて所へよね。}Yeah. I doubt this place has seen much action anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、あれは浜紀中の四天王なの。}It's the Hamaki's Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちが使ってればこの体育館も本望ね。}If we practice here, the gym might become amazing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうそう。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{敬子。}Kyouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って。}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見学園バレー部キャプテン。鮎原こずえです。}I'm Fujimi Academy volleyball club's captain, Ayuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{いつかどっかであったようだけど…}We've met before, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{…改めて、御挨拶するわ。}…let's have a proper introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは浜紀中キャプテンの、泉ゆり。\Nいずみ・ゆり}I'm Hamaki's captain. Izumi Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{工藤圭子ちゃん。\Nくどう・けいこ}Kudou Keiko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{小沢幸江。\Nおざわ・ゆきえ}Ozawa Yukie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{香取良子。\Nかとり・よしこ}Katori Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちのこと浜紀中の四天王だ何て言う人もいるようね。}Some people apparently call us The Big Four of Hamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・大学から)、あたしたちもここで練習すること成ったんで見にきたのよ。}We came to see if we could practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{学校が合併されたら、同じバレー部ね。}Since we're merging, we're in the same club, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{よろしく。}Let's work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ…}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう言われても、あんたたちのためによろしくできるかどうか。}I'm not really sure if we'll be able to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう言うことなの？}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちのバレーは厳しいのよ。}Our volleyball is intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。そう言うこと。}Yeah. There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちに付いてこれない。}I doubt you'll keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{なー何だって。}Wh- what…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと。もう一度言ってごらんよ。}Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{ナカ。}Naka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{私達のやり方でやくからさ。}We'll practice in our own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{付いてこれる人は付いてくれば良いじゃん。}If you keep up with us, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。合併されたら、あなたたちも富士見学園のバレー部でしょう。}Hmph. After merging with us, you're part of Fujimi's volleyball club, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{だったら、キャプテン鮎原さんのXXX。}You should obey captain Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは無理ね。}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、あたしたちあんたたちじゃ、実力は違いすぎるもの。}After all, the difference in our skills is too vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{喧嘩おる気なの？}Are you picking up a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{待ってよ。}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆XXXバカにされて。}Everyone's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って、待って。}Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆、辞めて。}Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなことじゃあたし、安心した卒業していけないわ。}I can't graduate with a peace of mind in such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆、合併して一緒なる仲間のはずじゃないの？}Doesn't merging mean we get to be friends with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし三年の桂城由美。いったいどうしたの？}I'm a third year student, Katsuragi Imi. What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは別に喧嘩なんかするつむりないわ。}We didn't intend to pick a fight with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併すれば、それは確かに一つのバレー部よ。}After the merge, we've became a single club indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{学園のバレー部として、頑張るわ。}We'll do our best as the club's members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちはあたしたちのバレーしかできないわ。}But we can do the volleyball in our own way only.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあたしたち…\Nーあたしたちのバレー？}- In our…\N- …own way only?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}- Let's head back.\N- Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{桂城さん、ごめんなさい。}Katsuragi-san, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{驚いたわ。}I'm surprised…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆睨み合ってすごいんだもの。}You were looking daggers so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{最終は色々難しいこともあるでしょう。けど、皆、お願いね。}It's going to be difficult, all right. But I urge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{立派なバレー部にXXXってね。}Please make a good club with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{安心して卒業していけるように。}That way I'll graduate with no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{おねがいよ。}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{《富士見学園中学校第３５回卒業式会場》}《35th graduation ceremony of Fujimi Academy middle school》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{では、無事卒業…おめでとう。}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{有り難う御座います。}Thank you very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{桂城さん、卒業おめでとう。}Katsuragi-san, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{あいがとう。}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆でバレー部の伝統守ってね。}Protect the club's tradition with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{おねがいね。}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちゃんとXXXして、強いチームを作ってね。}Make a great, strong team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫です。任しておいてください。}The club's safe in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{桂城さんは…富士見高校のバレー部に入るのね。}Katsuragi-san will probably join Fujimi high school volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしも来年は入るわ。}I'll join it next year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしもよ。}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張らなきゃ。}We need to do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張らなきゃ…}We need to do our best…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれは…}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見女子大のバレー部よ。}It's our girls university's club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、すごい。}Whoa, awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごい練習ね。}Amazing training…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX勇者しとことXXXですもの。}I've heard about them even before transferring here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{ー行ってみない？\Nーえ。}- Wanna try?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーおい。\Nーはい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、ちびっこ。}Right at you, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちびちゃん達。やるわね。}You've got what it takes, sweeties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見学園ね。}Fujimi Academy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部の鮎原こずえです。}I'm Ayuhara Kozue of the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川みどりです。}I'm Hayakawa Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテンの大原まりよ。}I'm their captain, Oohara Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごい。}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{二人共とてもいい素質を持ってるわ。}You both have very good qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう？よかったら、すこしやってみる？}Wanna play with us for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーよろしくおねがいします。\Nーよろしくおねがいします。}- Please treat us well.\N- Please treat us well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{いい？手加減しないわよ。}All right, I won't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{大変だわ。}Troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーね、明後日から春休みけど、どうするの？\Nーんん…}- Spring break started this morning. What are you going to do?\N- Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だ何も計画を立てていないの。}I still haven't decided anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{東京の家に帰るでしょう。}Won't you be going home, to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうね。}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうだ。}Ah, got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{大原さんのチームにXXXもらって、練習をしよう。}Let's talk to Oohara-san and practice with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{大学のチームに？}With university girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってくれるかしら。}Will she let us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、それは頼んでみなきゃ…}We'll have to ask…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン！}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン。一大事！バレー部の一大事よ。}Captain, troubles. A serious issue with the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの、そんなに慌てて？}Why are you flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{一大事じゃなんて、お袋にいつもXXXなんだから…}My mom always calls everything "a serious issue".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{なに言ってんの。}What are you saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{これが一大事と言うはなくて、何が一大事なの？}If this isn't serious, I don't know what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{乗り込んできたの。}They occupied the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{練習してるのよ。}They're practicing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中の四天王が…}The Hamaki's Big Four…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーえ？\Nーえ？}- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中学は立ち退いたのに、市のスポーツセンターができるんだって。}Since Hamaki came here, they said they can't use the city gym anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{それで(XXX・グランで)何かの工事がもう始まっていて…}And now that the other gym is under renovation…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{練習する場所は無くなっちゃったら死んだ。}…they got nowhere to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからこっちに行ったとわけなんだけど…}That's why they went to us…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{その練習は酷いのよ。}But their practice is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう丸で自分達だけのコート見たいにしてさ。}They act as if they owned the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{カッコやナカ達は？}What about Kakko and Naka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{桂城さんの卒業する時、絶対に喧嘩しないって誓ったでしょう？}They pledged not to fight till Katsuragi-san graduates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからじっと我慢してるわ。}Until now they were patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもいつまでもXXX分からない。早く。}But there's no telling what they do now. Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、キャプテン、大変！}Ah, captain, troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{あれ見てよ。}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{良い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーそれじゃ。\Nーおおおお。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちのコート…}Our court…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{しまってくれ(は良い・よい)。}Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{なにが四天王よ。}The Big Four, my foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{生意気ね。}How arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{待って、ナカ。}Hold on, Naka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。皆で一緒に練習しましょう。}Izumi-san, let's practice together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{未だあたしたちの練習は終わってないのよ。}We're still in the middle of the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{そこで待てって、ちょっと。}Just wait there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここは皆のコートよ。}This is everyones' court.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆で一緒にやればいいでしょう。}It's okay if we all do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{ヘ。}Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{邪魔なんだな。}You're getting in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かんないだな。}You just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたち一緒ことよ邪魔なんだよ。}If we practice with you, you'll only hinder us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{暇だったら、球拾いでもしてよ。}If you're free, go fetch a ball or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{その方がお似合いよ。}That's fitting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうそう。}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？皆良い子ちゃん、だからさ。}You're all good girls after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{ハハハハハ。}Hahahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ、みどりさん。}Ah, Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{やったわね。}Now you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{喧嘩なら、相手なるよ。}If you wanna fight, we'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{畜生。XXXなって。}Damn. How shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん、何てこと…}Midori-san, what did you do…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって…こんなにXXXだって、黙ってるつもり？}Do you want to stay silent when they make fun of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{黙ってするつもりはないわ。}I don't intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{喧嘩しようと言うの。}So you do want to fight us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{こうなったら、仕方ないわね。}All right. It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいえ。}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{このボールで決めるのよ。}We'll settle it with this ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？それは面白いわ。}Heh, how interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{これでどっちに力があるか、はっきりするわね。}We'll finally figure who's stronger, no buts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{四人制で勝負しましょうよ。}Let's do a four players match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{四人制って、あんたたちは知ってる？}Do you know how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{バカにしないで。}Don't look down on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX選手がよく練習に使うだとことぐらいわ。}We used to practice in such system before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレーだって、知ってるわ。}We know that much, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは結構ね。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、始めましょうか。}Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたち四天王に、挑戦するなんか、あんなで履行じゃないね。}Though it's not very challenging if it is you who challenge us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの高慢な花を必勝ってやるわ。}We'll win with these arrogant missies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{よ、君達。}You girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{私が審判をしよう。}I'll be your referee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{梶岡先生。}Professor Kajioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{私は浜紀中学バレー部のコーチをしてる、梶岡だ。よろしく。}I'm Hamaki volleyball club's coach, Kajioka. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{合併したら、私は君達の面倒を見ることなるだろうね。}After the merge, looks like I'll take care of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちには本郷先生が…}But we have professor Hongou…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{私は浜紀中学のチームを育てて、優勝決定戦まで行った。}I led Hamaki's team to the championship finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{新しいチームのコーチも、当然私が引き受ける。}It's only natural that I become your coach as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはいつ決まったんですか。}When was that decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーあ、先生！\Nー先生！}- Ah, professor!\N- Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷です。}I'm Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{では…梶岡です。}Ah… I'm Kajioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ…決まったって言うわけじゃないんだが、そうなるかもしれないって言うことでしてね。}Err… it wasn't decided, but that's not to say it couldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生を呼んできたの方がよかったでしょう？}Good that I called him over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{今までのことは皆話しておいたわ。}I filled him with the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝負するのね。頑張ってね。}You're holding a game, no? Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、そう言うことで、本郷先生のチームの力を見ておきたいと思いましてね、}Now that you said it, I want to see the strength of professor Hongou's team…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あの…審判は…}But… about refereeing…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{私がやってもいいですね。}Is it all right if I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうぞ。}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生、あの…バレーは…コーチを何年ぐらいXXX?}Professor, how many years have you been coaching volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいえ。本校に来て、始めてばかりです。}Well, I started only recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうですか。私もう五年に成りますかね。}Is that so? I've been coaching for five years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{嫌らしいなね。}How spiteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、サーブ権を決めなさい。}Well then, decide the serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーじゃんけん。\Nーじゃんけん。}- Rock, paper.\N- Rock, paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{こっちのサーブね。}We'll serve first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{試合開始。}Begin the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張って！}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・先生)!}Show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{おう！}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{任して！}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{ドンマイドンマイ！}Don't mind, don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{ごめん。}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{始めて見たわ、あんな変化球。}I haven't seen such a curve ball before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{この(XXX・バッチ)にいただきましょう。}Let's keep this pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかりね。}Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・プレー)よ！}It comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどり！}Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Nice going, nice going. We'll end it in to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン！}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXないわ。}Don't strain yourself, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・軽い、軽い・華麗、華麗)！}How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{はるかに力が違う。}They're on a different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けるかもしれない。}We might lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張れ。}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{出きるところまでやるんだ。}You keep at it till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達と私は一緒にバレーを始めた。}Me and you girls started it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{どこまでできるか戦って行こう。}Fight with all you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張るんだ。}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{やるわ。}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン。}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張るのよ。}Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、さ、さ、さ、さ。}Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・軽い、軽い・華麗、華麗)。}Too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXXセットXXXもいただきましょう。}Let's win and get the gym already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの？}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{以上。}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ーおい！\Nーいいな。}- Hey!\N- Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、痛い…}Ow, it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{いただきましょう。}Let's get the serve back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{チャンス、チャンス、チャンス。}Chance, chance, chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{あと一点でお終いよ。}One more point and it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{いかん。}No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{ふふふ。}Fufufu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちの力を分かったでしょう。}Do you understand our power now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、来るよ！}It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン！}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{どう？問題じゃないわね？}How is it? No more complaints, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・前半戦)に成らないわ。}I guess we won't be seeing you in the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね…大変ないわ…}Too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けた。}We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{完敗だ。}Complete defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、未だ一緒に初めよ。}But we can start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{次の目標に…新しい力に向かって。}Move on to the next goal… acquire new strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達のコーチはこの私はする。}I will be coaching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、試合終了だ。}Now then, the match's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{よくやった。}You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちが新しいバレー部を作ってけばいいわね。}We can start a new club here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張ろうよ。ね？}Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{悔しい。}How vexing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{悔しいけど…}It's vexing, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは負けたんだ。}…we lost through and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{負けたのね。}We lost it…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX力が違う何て…}For our power to be so different…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはやる。}I'll go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{きっとやってみせるわ。}I'll surely show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、もう行くの?}Oh, are you going so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{折角の春休みだって言うのに…}The long-awaited spring break is here…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{言い出したら、聞かないんだから。}But you don't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{気を付けてね。}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{欲しいものあったら、電話してね。}If you need anything, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、行ってらっしゃい。}Be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{合宿なんて始めてだわ。}It's first time I go to a training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{それも、大学のバレー部の合宿なんて…すごく厳しいだろうな。}On top of it, it's an university training camp. It must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{悔しい。}How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{四天王になんか負けるもんか。}I won't lose to The Big Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんとしても、実力を付けて帰るわ。}I'll attain new power without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:22:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{キャプテン大原さん特別に許可をいただいたんだ…}Now that I got a special permission from captain Oohara…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:22:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみる。}I see a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{自分のバレーがどこまでできるか。}How far can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{やってみるわ。}I'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{ゴホン。}Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{この席は開いてますか。}Is this seat free?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうぞ。}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ふふ。}Fufu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、みどりさん。}Hey, Midori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしも行くわ。}I am going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{大学の合宿にね。}To the university training camp, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま…どうして分かったの？}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かるわよ。}It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんは「何をしよう」とする勘ぐられば。}You had that "what should I do" look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしもキャプテン大原さんに電話をして頼むんだのよ。}I called captain Oohara-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{「鮎原さんは電話した」直ぐアウトだったそうよ。}She told me about your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうして、電車の時間は叔母様から。}Then your aunt disclosed the departure time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさん。}Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん、一緒にやりましょう。}Ayuhara-san, let's fight together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{どんなに厳しい合宿でも。}No matter how tough it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{やるわ。}We'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしはきっとやってみせるわ。}I'll show them how to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉ユリの変化球サーブXXXを胸に秘め(る)。}While Izumi Yuri's curve ball technique remains a secret…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:24:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえ・みどりアタックコンビは富士見大学女子バレー部の合宿に参加した。}…Kozue-Midori attack duo participates in Fujimi all-girls university volleyball training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{彼女XX目的はなんであると見抜いたキャプテンの大原は…}Captain Oohara, seeing through their goal right away…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{中学生といえども、容赦無くXXX。}…doesn't go easy, even though they're middle schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{挫けそうに成る二人に大原の叱責はとる。}About to collapse, they get reprimanded by Oohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{だが、二人は練習に必死に耐える。}But they endure the training desperately.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.02,0:24:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{ついに、変化球サーブXXXの飛球を身につけるだ。}Finally, they start seeing through the curve ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
